yCastle upstream tests for JCEDH. It feels a bit like trial and error! There’s a lot to consider, but inspecting those tests might give me some clarity on how to proceed.", "thinkingSignature": "{\"id\":\"rs_0f7747aecb615386016a10d9db26e48192a7051c5fca5f6b0f\",\"type\":\"reasoning\",\"encrypted_content\":\"gAAAAABqENntYrHC3RNCSsD0Yc2Nj3BuUnBACgusVgxjKq14gCmyEh0orijNl8X_ad4CPADqvg_sSH4PLI2T_7ef8rdQWPLP6mZ5t30n4fZuRT9GbPudXPmUf0R50yNzwYJJFoSv-8AGmvIiMpDV3rdCsOZVtBMTxkj0Bjsw6NjlBkbpls5eQ76sv3ldJI0qSh6P_hufQMNOOK_a_PK_X54k0u0l95f8cvXawp7w2ac9s33llnXC8W9IwOpb9PnpvncrCAyhGGHdSTF6k2zpTschHCl4kQv2t8xJs3PWMmjNQ9pQfE2h5r69IvKHYTU6PZsynyNB1fpX8sAZYycZhkeaEeIOdszU6fmkFwb-bqLSgNmUg9frlT_4cDxEDMZ7Hlly4G4-R0C7XFluN5i2YtSiPKe_oljtejt11MgCl9ASeDX5PefzCBEE6VFiehVbehPlTNxlEa1ypDwUVcFVHGGM24G6f6WmFKElY4coSh-Id-msaO8wXyFoGiWglF4j56JTRwGibWr6YfndP3kesBDnwKD5zzPZNyOeRDyjKYovRaxKblbu9afevEjm3OHHr1cPZg4ULFJAm52nUgqIvd_7JA4jQpei_RqxAsTp_T8_6oCSWGWZTxqXsKGPI08elbJ-ZI3kt9d0WxGMFr3O8lq8dtAXonKTbUB3D175qos9DTjoikH0WiPgiF6HsiBwmomhlWuP2Q0kAJCOxI-Qo48ERJlakkKNc6MdSTbTzRQJina94x5zrT025ZRrQLOMmz5obJM1qtyYFeoe7kLxnHFSpENjGoahlsjYB0Qdurhy7cBnFpfQE-6QTd5zA52w8XX12LteIRU1KoGYLEs0gPsGiWEa9Mw7QyytgdU_TienC45EviECTudgi3_nARpTMFQR24kf2At-NSKwOS1MmdAVaBRcXxgnfuCPMMvLPNBGOc2qtJ6DcVAEnNJAG9ff_U5RpdJkEe6x2xulmaUQyGTBmUdupmv_oZd0QDpWqPVGz2EEbdJT3RGLL7eiXrBn5qs9e1SfzA1xwXXUKE6bBwFKnbtS6sfD2k9Oujb8QoP9ValO21M_Sla05UkiVYQmH_5k9PfCt-NwAgOIjxjMslyjKZf6qI5o6AnyxmItuC0At_F9R7dwAi-pcDrLMG6zVGlPSLXal_0qjlSJuTnPnZv_7lYYltjSXgXQC_2dHLiCq2Q9LThNnOV0xnTELkH7NUyJ5ol0EoWALNjuzc8u1vVApIJZb-kYC1S3k9DmDtTAtys0e9sGJEQWyZoDP-iEqI36MB51MlMIFrGRuWbD7KHi2r3s9hKPAdWQMQHZeL53fI0TIKLxlBry8ccEM1kB5b7i14A_rtfYOog8BTkNxq5qyTHNpHOjWskYway4ENDWmXY6qxDbJFwpSHtexkHbiC5MkpHxM2yHCqVCGBUlgngR633rC12rawqHj0eys8Dq74AhHW31vsGODoHrlIjhjU_wWtu4teiHSMLR_IBntXPLUFZl88dw_g52aVPxWIeh1cxp18n08ooq7wbvBYw9mW_7A3tS3wGQtLW57ca26VvVaXx3r970RtWHdEWJblgwoVVPFPYwPYXzbMDFwnjf60jjlXtZJX7vEEmAk3XuYgw7pxjldo2xTIZg6wxeRqLEOyzW6I0XUCZOVFPYxSkica6BKlqjTLbuLMzHiiicWc_Xwocl