[thinking] 
[thinking] I’m thinking about checking the test report, though it might not be relevant. Perhaps the active report from the previous attempt indicates no new findings since they didn’t use our patch. I need to make some changes, like maybe combining it into the existing file. I could consider generating real JCEDHPublicKey serialization bytes at the test startup using the serialization’s constructor, but I’m realizing that might not work. If Native Image lacks serialization metadata, that could lead to problems during deserialization.
